  "text": "AI nespasí vaši produktivitu. AI nespasí váš byznys.\n\n„Having your team type in `import openai` doesn't mean you are at the cutting-edge of AI no matter how you embarrass yourself on LinkedIn…“ 😀\n\nČlánek pro všechny, kteří právě teď točí kormidlem, aby byli co nejvíc #AI 🔥\n\n„Your business will be disrupted exactly as hard as it'd have been if you had done nothing, and much worse than it'd have been if you just got your fundamentals right.“\n\n„Everyone is talking about Retrieval Augmented Generation, but most companies don't actually have any internal docs worth retrieving. Fix. Your. Shit.“\n\nNo, přečtěte si to sami.",
